testcase.name: It applies a fixed Xor algorithm when given a hex string and equally long hex secret
It applies a fixed Xor algorithm when given a hex string of 69 and a secret of F3
It applies a fixed Xor algorithm when given a longer hex string and secret
It applies a fixed Xor algorithm when given 123A and AAAA and returns B890
It applies a fixed Xor to 1b37373331363f78151b7f2b783431333d78397828372d363c78373e783a393b3736 with a key of X
It applies a fixed Xor to 7b5a4215415d544115415d5015455447414c155c46155f4058455c5b523f with a key of 5
It applies a repeating-key Xor to 1b37373331363f78151b7f2b783431333d78397828372d363c78373e783a393b3736 with a key of X
It applies a repeating-key Xor to 7b5a4215415d544115415d5015455447414c155c46155f4058455c5b523f with a key of 5
It applies a repeating-key Xor to the sample file
